short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Viewer for ZenFS in Chrome Devtools

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
DISCLAIMER: ZenFS Viewer is an unofficial, community-developed Chrome DevTools extension. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by the official ZenFS project.

ZenFS Viewer is a Chrome DevTools extension that helps developers inspect and analyze ZenFS file systems. With this extension, you can:

View ZenFS file system structure directly in Chrome DevTools
Monitor file operations and access patterns
Debug storage-related issues in real-time
Analyze ZenFS performance metrics
Export file system data for further analysis
